OL,3,CConservatives to scrap plans to ban
OL,4,Cnew petrol and diesel cars by 2030
OL,6,F"The reality is that the EU's change
OL,7,Fof heart on EVs will leave Labour even
OL,8,Fmore isolated, and by pressing ahead
OL,9,Falone, we are placing our domestic
OL,10,Findustry at a disadvantage while
OL,11,Fgiving others the opportunity to
OL,12,Fdominate global supply chains," wrote
OL,13,FBadenoch.
OL,15,F"The only winners in this economy are
OL,16,FChina, who have happily profited from
OL,17,Four decision to accelerate demand for
OL,18,Felectric vehicles without first
OL,19,Fsecuring our own battery and mineral
OL,20,Fsupply chains," she said.
