OL,3,CConservatives to scrap plans to ban
OL,4,Cnew petrol and diesel cars by 2030
OL,6,FThe column followed Badenoch's meeting
OL,7,Fwith Italian Prime Minister Giorgia
OL,8,FMeloni, who has lobbied the EU to
OL,9,Fwater down its own plans.
OL,11,FSix EU countries, including Meloni and
OL,12,FPoland's Prime Minister Donald Tusk,
OL,13,Frecently called on the EU to rethink
OL,14,Fits 2035 ban, saying it could hurt
OL,15,Findustrial competitiveness.
OL,17,FBadenoch argued that scrapping the ban
OL,18,Fwould "bring the UK back into line
OL,19,Fwith other global markets" and give
OL,20,Fbusinesses "freedom" to be guided by
OL,21,Fconsumer demand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
