OL,6,F"Most importantly, scrapping the
OL,7,Fmandate will give us the space to
OL,8,Frebuild our car industry. A
OL,9,FConservative approach will support
OL,10,Finnovation, not force it through
OL,11,Fregulation that ignores economic
OL,12,Freality," she said.
