OL,3,CConservatives to scrap plans to ban
OL,4,Cnew petrol and diesel cars by 2030
OL,6,F"By ending the mandate, we can
OL,7,Fprioritise research and development
OL,8,Fwhere the UK has real competitive
OL,9,Fadvantages. It will enable us to
OL,10,Fsupport advances in next-generation
OL,11,Fautomotive technologies, including
OL,12,Fhybrids, hydrogen and other low-
OL,13,Femission options that give consumers
OL,14,Fproper choice."
OL,16,FPlans to ban the sale of petrol and
OL,17,Fdiesel cars were first introduced by
OL,18,Fformer Conservative prime minister
OL,19,FBoris Johnson and were opposed at the
OL,20,Ftime by Badenoch, then a cabinet
OL,21,Fmember.
