OL,3,CConservatives to scrap plans to ban
OL,4,Cnew petrol and diesel cars by 2030
OL,6,FIn the recent Budget, Chancellor
OL,7,FRachel Reeves announced that drivers
OL,8,Fof battery electric cars will be
OL,9,Fcharged 3p per mile for the Electric
OL,10,FVehicle Excise Duty from April 2028.
OL,12,FThis is in response to a huge
OL,13,Freduction in revenue from fuel duty as
OL,14,Fmore drivers switch from petrol or
OL,15,Fdiesel cars to EVs.
OL,17,FShe also extended grants for the
OL,18,Fpurchase of new EVs until 2030.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
