OL,3,CConservatives to scrap plans to ban
OL,4,Cnew petrol and diesel cars by 2030
OL,6,FSome 39,965 new pure battery electric
OL,7,Fcars were registered last month, the
OL,8,FSociety of Motor Manufacturers and
OL,9,FTraders (SMMT) said.
OL,11,FThat was up 3.6% from November 2024,
OL,12,Fwhich was the smallest year-on-year
OL,13,Fincrease since December 2023, when
OL,14,Fregistrations declined by 34.2%.
OL,16,FThat sharp fall was attributed to
OL,17,Fsupply chain issues and a stronger-
OL,18,Fthan-usual December 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
