OL,6,FSMMT chief executive Mike Hawes said:
OL,7,F"Even in a fragile market, zero
OL,8,Femission vehicle uptake continues to
OL,9,Frise, which is exactly what we need.
OL,11,F"But the weakest growth for almost two
OL,12,Fyears - ahead of Government announcing
OL,13,Fa new tax on EVs (electric vehicles) -
OL,14,Fshould be seen as a wake-up call that
OL,15,Fsustained increase in demand for EVs
OL,16,Fcannot be taken for granted."
